text: Downs Farm (or Downs Farms) is a neighborhood located within Cherry Hill in Camden County, New Jersey, United States. Downs Farm Swim Club is a private swim club located on Haddonfield-Berlin Road (County Route 561). It was founded in 1964 and contains 3 separate pools.About Downs Farm Swim Club ==References== Category:Neighborhoods in Cherry Hill, New Jersey
